  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-04 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. Model Risk Level 3. Seven of thirteen credibility factors are fully assessed; two factors (Numerical solver error, Equivalency of input parameters) are marked not-assessed with rationale citing scope limitations. The unassessed factors materially weaken credibility at MRL 3 but the package decision records Accepted, embedding weakener W-EP-04.",
